CWC simple api for incoming mail from third party vendors

== xml validation
the main document is the cwc_schema.rnc the .rng and xsd documents are generated using trang (http://www.thaiopensource.com/relaxng/trang.html)

== changes from 1.0 to 2.0 (api)

* CamelCase schema
* Tweak the schema to be more in line with the spec
* V2 api always returns xml formatted error message on the rest points that accept XML as input
* XML API for the CRM vendors to retrieve emails
* XML/JSON API for the Advocacy Vendors to retrieve messages they have sent (by apikey)
* Improved documentation
